data.description: Fall in love with this unique historic home on a large corner lot with wrap around porch. This home was updated with lots of wood accents, updated kitchen with large bar, built in Oven and Microwave and pantry. The large living area is open to the beautiful dining area which also is adorned with a decorative wood ceiling. This open concept living,dining,kitchen also has 3 roomy bedrooms with lots of closet storage. 2 of the bedrooms share a Pullman bath with it's own hot water tank. This wonderful home has a large fenced yard, carport
